{"tid":2012090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一email，支持香港電台!","createTime":"2020-05-11T12:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T12:18:32.000Z","uid":260366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2d34cb99b934c38efbc200d660dfe24151275ae0","tid":2012090,"uid":260366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"致：香港電台 ccu@rthk.hk、商務及經濟發展局 ccibenq@cedb.gov.hk 及廣播處長梁家榮 kwleung@rthk.hk<br />\n<br />\n今日立法會資訊科技及廣播事務委員會會議討論香港電台的管治！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTemplate（僅供參考， 建議加入個人意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n敬啟者：<br />\n<br />\n您好，本人今天看到立法會資訊科技及廣播事務委員會會議，在討論香港電台的管治時，邱局長並沒有對香港電台收到的讚賞作出肯定，本人深感失望。<br />\n本人認為 廣播處長梁家榮盡忠職守，港台多個節目例如《頭條新聞》、鏗鏘集等製作認真，令人十分滿意。 港台是公營電台，公帑是來自香港市民，港台為香港人發聲並無不妥。<br />\n<br />\n言論自由乃是香港基石。本人十分欣賞和感謝港台的節目講良心話，維護香港人的核心價值，本人期望政府須向港台提供足夠資源，支持這一個受廣大香港市民支持和愛戴的香港電台，並且應對其作出表揚及肯定！<br />\n<br />\n香港市民 敬啟 <br />\n<br />\n日期"},{"pid":"9519d5889ac37c8322db20c6b081c93759f005cb","tid":2012090,"uid":260366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cdf93a96f6264482d25f136a32c843b8781e3f0","tid":2012090,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a778826b03c4b826acd47e16d5c4269a2d6d2fae","tid":2012090,"uid":278085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:18:32.000Z","msg":"今日話港台收視勁低 其實叫屋企人平日長開電視 開港台唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n資訊性又強 質素又高 仲睇乜9 cctvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}